flowchart TB
    JobsStore[(Jobs Store<br/>schedules + state)]
    Scheduler[Scheduler Service<br/>tick + leader election]
    Coord[Coordination Service<br/>leader election]
    Queue[(Durable Job Queue)]
    Workers[Worker Pool<br/>lease + execute]
    Leases[(Lease Cache<br/>TTL = job timeout)]
    History[(Status / History Store)]
    Alerts[Notifications / Alerts]

    JobsStore --> Scheduler
    Coord <--> Scheduler
    Scheduler -->|enqueue due jobs| Queue
    Queue --> Workers
    Workers <-->|acquire lease| Leases
    Workers -->|update status| History
    Workers -.->|on failure| Alerts

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Scheduler,Workers,Alerts service
    class JobsStore,Queue,Leases,History store
    class Coord config
